And then is there anything else you'd like to share at all?

00:42:18.000 --> 00:42:25.000
No, it's lovely questions.

00:42:25.000 --> 00:42:29.000
It reminds me a lot of things.

00:42:29.000 --> 00:42:32.000
And good memories.

00:42:32.000 --> 00:42:34.000
And that's all.

